    {
      "name": "Scions of the Storm",
      "description": "Yndrasta and your Annihilators unit are not set up during the deployment phase. Instead, from the third battle round onwards, they can use Lightning-Strike Arrival: set up anywhere on the battlefield more than 6\" from all enemy units.",
